The child doctor said

3
00:00:13.600 --> 00:00:15.966
If I abort the baby

4
00:00:15.966 --> 00:00:18.300
I will never have children again

5
00:00:18.300 --> 00:00:22.366
Uncle, what should I do?

6
00:00:23.533 --> 00:00:24.366
uncle

7
00:00:25.566 --> 00:00:28.066
Xiaoxiao, since you like children

8
